  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he-- he and several others started a partisan group in the area.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We-- we got out into the forest in the-- in the summer of 1942.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But that September, my grandfather, who was religious and wanted to go back to the ghetto for the high holidays, went back.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My uncle Chaim was in the forest with the partisans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But my younger-- the younger son, Sana, went with him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that-- they liquidated the ghetto on Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My uncle Sana was made, with other younger men, to dig the ditches.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my grandfather was shot while running away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My uncle was put on a truck to go to the trains.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he-- he and another and a cousin of his got away in the melee.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he joined my other uncle as a partisan in the forests.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Right around that time, my uncle Chaim came back to where we were living in the forest.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And what-- what we did at that time is to make like a room underground so that during the daytime, if anybody wandered through the forest, you-- it looked like there was no one there.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we would come out at night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he came one day and he said that he had found a couple who would keep me, that we-- he had paid them with our household goods, that-- whatever we had-- he had taken out of the ghetto little by little on all-- on all the times that were when he was getting in and out, and I could go and live with them in the open, where I wouldn't have to live underground.",
      "word_count": 75
    }
  ],
